Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't die?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.07,0:00:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal... Devens!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw... a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I vowed to protect her. I promised to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.93,0:00:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, I wasn't there when she was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, I thought that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it wasn't the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one who fired that shot yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.15,0:01:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal joined Inferno... as a sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Huang,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to think that you're accepting me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.39,0:01:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as your sworn brother on your memorable birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is such a delightful surprise for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xu, don't be so modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took me too long to praise your achievement of establishing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your turf in western Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the not. so. distant future, eastern Japan will be in our hands as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:01:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:02:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's toast to our future, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Godo Family wants us to kill Xu, the head of the Chinese mafia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it necessary to target the old geezer, Huang, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He supports one of Inferno's rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he looked after you after you got kicked out of Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... knows too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you no sense of honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep your honor. I'm different from you. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Gregor, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gregor Unit is in position. We can go in anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay put and await orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't eager about this operation in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:03:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do it without her. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True. This task may not be for her as it's just providing cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gregor, we'll carry out the operation as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Parker Unit, go in through the back door and take care of the guards first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'd say that it'll be about 3 minutes before they smoke Huang and Xu out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she can do it within 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What the hell is she doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is the most efficient and logical method.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in Japan! Causing such a serious incident will...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's Japan or the US the value of life... is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Master Huang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who on earth is making such a daring attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can think of one possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Scythe's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was none other than I who helped that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how he repays my kindness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kindness? What does that mean again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Huang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You've got guts. You're still not giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like that. I'll go along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like playing games?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot when the music ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you make a fool of me! Whatever organization you're from,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't think that you can get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You don't know me, do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:07:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being in the underworld, you've at least heard that name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can win here, I bet the whole world will throw themselves at your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your next life, try to pick a better job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adios, Chink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who got her started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I taught her how to kill... and led her to the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up her life... with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The arrangements for our escape will be completed soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to see an acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come in contact with Zwei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hunt them in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're next... Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji, you went home early yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, uhm, when I went to see Sanae after school yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were already gone, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I had some errands to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to pry or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... the weather forecast didn't say anything about snow, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty... isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys made quite a big show, Ms. Garland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The security police are on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend that those who participated in last night's attack
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leave the country as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about it, as most of them have already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear that. In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate that you killed Xu without leaving any evidence whatsoever
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Godo Family's involvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I hope that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you let me know your plans next time you operate in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a difficult mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If things had gone as planned, no one would've gone home in a coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault. When she didn't... When Phantom didn't show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've anticipated something like that would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so hard on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that Drei has some issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can understand where she's coming from. She feels impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't properly taken over the title of Phantom yet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as she didn't battle it out with the previous Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once Drei truly wins the status of Phantom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she will probably become suitably calm and composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, as long as she brings down Zwei with her own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't bring your lunch today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but, Motegi... how did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do you wanna go to the cafeteria with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, but what about your lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate it after second period.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Motegi, in recognition of your notable service today,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby allow you to sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes ma'am! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there. Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. You're the unpopular Motegi, right? My brother told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you tell her about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? You sold me out, didn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Share your happiness with me. Just a little will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Brother, something like this isn't too bad once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to think that Elen and I have the same opinion. I feel honored!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we get along well after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Cal can't do anything in a crowd... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this seat for me. I'll go buy lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Meal B!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The urgent matter that Reiji had to attend to the other day was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were some home matters I really wanted to discuss with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I knew he was out on a date with you, Mio, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-it wasn't a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... if that was the case, you should have said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was kind of embarrassed, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how a girl's mind works!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy like that should be punished by losing some food... Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you eating it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're the one who gets all the happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dense! You still don't get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are tons of people in this world starving for happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Motegi here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked to give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I've got to go for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My junior wants me to do something for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My little bit of happiness is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little would do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go make sure she doesn't get mixed up with the wrong guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen is popular among boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're always worried about her, you won't survive, you obsessed brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go. She's your only sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'll make it up to you some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about making it up to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You're capable of killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not because you've been ordered to, nor because you're cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But simply of your own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one characteristic of yours that deserves a special mention... Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Ein are different, since you were driven by pure murderous intent
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while her mind was strengthened by a cheap brainwash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, you are a failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you still suggested a new direction for my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried... exploring the theme of hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:18:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen... my proud third work... Drei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to Cal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make a long story short, I did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No brainwashing. No hypnotic suggestions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't manipulate her memory or emotions at all, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thoroughly refined...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her natural hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice of you to have left such a person of talent to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot but appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scythe... You alone I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't forgive? Do you detest me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't kill me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent self control.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have both pure hatred and the ability to make levelheaded judgements.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful balance you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:19:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that sense, Drei goes a little overboard. She can't control herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at least she seems to have enough sense to avoid crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she seems to at least have enough sense to avoid crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go help, you'd better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will interrupt us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do, Ein?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:20:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say ex-Phantom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived until this day in order to hunt down and kill that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
